{
  "stem": "13213.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We started immediately working with some Italian mechanics which were, were actually hired by the Israeli government to work on the overhaul of motors for the B-17 and the spitfires.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was trained to work on the motors for the B-17, which was a radial engine made by Pratt and Whitney.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was studying on my own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And with the help of the Italian mechanics, in no time, many of us became qualified, good mechanics.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the Italians were later on let go, and we took over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Most of the Israeli guys took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was very happy to be in the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were going to the city, visiting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I made some friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the only thing that many of the guys had families-- sisters, brothers, or somebody, to go to for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I didn't have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But this friend of mine used to take me to his parents'.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "His parents-- Asha Kruger, his parents were just arrived from Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they were in a [NON-ENGLISH] Israel refugee camp, or immigrant camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they were quite nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I met many other people that were very nice to me and used to invite me for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When I finished the Kheil HaAvir, there were many jobs available for mechanics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I applied to El Al.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "El Al hired me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I started to work as an aircraft mechanic in El Al.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Sent to some courses to bring up to date with the civil aviation, and DC-4 aircraft and constellation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "At that time, they just purchased some constellation airplanes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were studying those airplanes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the time I haven't had any family except, while I was in the Air Force, I forgot to mention, I heard a name mentioned, Waks.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
